1
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:52,870
Adeng, this is bad.

2
00:00:52,950 --> 00:00:56,280
The emperor and Qin Chong are coming after us with their men.

3
00:00:58,620 --> 00:01:01,500
Adeng, stop making useless struggles.

4
00:01:01,950 --> 00:01:03,480
If you insist on resisting,

5
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:07,160
you'll be reduced to ashes along with the secret realm.

6
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:09,539
I must take back the soul lamp,

7
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:10,580
awaken the Demon Lord,

8
00:01:10,580 --> 00:01:13,200
and restart the great cause of the Demon Clan. Hahaha.

9
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:16,130
What they have always wanted are me and the soul lamp.

10
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:20,250
I will not run away again this time,

11
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:23,230
nor will I let anyone get hurt because of me.

12
00:01:54,750 --> 00:01:57,280
Charge and flatten the Medicine King Valley!

13
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:59,330
Whoever seizes the bronze soul lamp

14
00:01:59,330 --> 00:02:03,660
will be rewarded with ten thousand gold and a fief of ten thousand households!

15
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:01,040
Master.

16
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:03,830
Silly child.

17
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:08,450
Don't cry. Remember that a healer's benevolent heart

18
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:10,750
can also slay demons

19
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,780
and protect the mortal world.

20
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:19,290
Ah...

21
00:04:50,330 --> 00:04:53,000
The Creation God could have sacrificed himself to protect the three realms.

22
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,730
Why did he forge this soul lamp?

23
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:10,000
To guide the lamp master and suppress the evil master.

24
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,330
The gate of the Myriad Demons Spirit Realm has opened.

25
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:15,080
I have been waiting for you here for a thousand years.
